Invocation Name: autochartist
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Autochartist is the global leader in automated financial market analysis. The service provides technical analysis and statistical analysis of financial markets. This analysis includes identification of breakouts of technical chart patterns, approaching and breakouts of support and resistance levels, as well as identification of exceptionally large market movements.

Your email address will be requested during the installation process in order for us to provide you with more details about our products and services.
